because your mom is nothing
more than a burned-out whore?

00:09:54.129 --> 00:09:57.534 position:5% line:77% align:start
Or good thing your brother bit
the dust while under
anesthesia? That part?

00:09:58.100 --> 00:09:59.401 position:33% line:89% align:start
You bastard!

00:09:59.636 --> 00:10:00.302 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hey, hold...

00:10:05.074 --> 00:10:05.907 position:44% line:89% align:start
on.

00:10:07.075 --> 00:10:07.610 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:10:07.976 --> 00:10:08.244 position:41% line:89% align:start
You-!

00:10:08.776 --> 00:10:09.110 position:27% line:89% align:start
(ADOLF) <i>Enough.</i>

00:10:10.679 --> 00:10:14.415 position:5% line:77% align:start
Picking fights with each other
because you can't handle the
pressure, huh?

00:10:17.418 --> 00:10:20.421 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Most of you are going to die on</i>
 <i>this mission, anyway.</i>

00:10:20.754 --> 00:10:21.489 position:33% line:89% align:start
[grumbling]

00:10:22.557 --> 00:10:25.259 position:5% line:89% align:start
Once a vermin, always a vermin.

00:10:25.593 --> 00:10:27.027 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:10:38.437 --> 00:10:42.108 position:7% line:83% align:start
(SHEILA) <i>I'm sorry, I have to</i>
 <i>apologize for my teammate.</i>

00:10:42.742 --> 00:10:45.444 position:7% line:89% align:start
(JASON) <i>I...I just lost it...</i>

00:10:47.713 --> 00:10:53.619 position:10% line:71% align:start
(SHEILA) <i>Look, everyone's on</i>
 <i>edge...But  anyway, thank you</i>
 <i>for trying  to help. Um, You're</i>
 <i>Russian, right?</i>

00:10:54.185 --> 00:10:57.589 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm Ivan. Please, don't you
worry about me!

00:10:58.189 --> 00:11:03.961 position:10% line:77% align:start
I'm always doing stuff like
this. My sister says I must be
some kind of idiot... [teehee]

00:11:04.295 --> 00:11:04.962 position:38% line:89% align:start
[titter]

00:11:05.530 --> 00:11:06.297 position:19% line:89% align:start
[exhales and inhales]

00:11:07.666 --> 00:11:08.465 position:10% line:83% align:start
(SHEILA) <i>Well, not everyone</i>
 <i>would've done what you did.</i>

00:11:09.266 --> 00:11:10.668 position:13% line:83% align:start
I think it took a lot of
courage.

00:11:18.542 --> 00:11:21.978 position:7% line:83% align:start
Huh! [snort] Could you be any
more obvious?!

00:11:22.645 --> 00:11:23.980 position:21% line:89% align:start
Love at first sight.

00:11:24.180 --> 00:11:24.580 position:38% line:89% align:start
[teehee]

00:11:26.316 --> 00:11:29.419 position:7% line:77% align:start
Careful, Ivan, if you fall in
love with Sheila, you're in for
a really rough road.

00:11:29.786 --> 00:11:34.156 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>I mean, you do know that she's </i>
 <i>got a thing for the captain! </i>
(laughter)

00:11:34.189 --> 00:11:34.990 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:11:39.394 --> 00:11:41.730 position:27% line:89% align:start
Uhhh...Oh, uh...

00:11:42.531 --> 00:11:44.298 position:7% line:83% align:start
You didn't hear that from me,
though!

00:11:44.332 --> 00:11:44.999 position:30% line:89% align:start
(EVA) <i>Too late!</i>

00:11:45.734 --> 00:11:46.167 position:5% line:89% align:start
(SHEILA) <i>How did you know that?</i>

00:11:47.435 --> 00:11:49.805 position:13% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Uh, well, I think</i>
 <i>Michelle mentioned it...</i>

00:11:49.837 --> 00:11:52.340 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>But then...how did she know?</i>

00:11:53.174 --> 00:11:55.175 position:5% line:89% align:start
(ALEX) <i>Hey dude, you all right?</i>

00:11:57.110 --> 00:11:57.578 position:69% line:89% align:start
I'm fine.

00:11:59.814 --> 00:12:01.681 position:7% line:83% align:start
I-I'm more of a man than him,
anyway.

00:12:03.249 --> 00:12:06.252 position:7% line:89% align:start
I know. Wanna play some catch?

00:12:06.286 --> 00:12:06.686 position:27% line:89% align:start
(MARCOS) <i>Sure...</i>

00:12:39.851 --> 00:12:42.820 position:35% line:83% align:start
AZARA CITY
SAITAMA PREFECTURE

00:12:46.857 --> 00:12:48.692 position:38% line:89% align:start
3 HOURS

00:12:48.725 --> 00:12:51.628 position:35% line:89% align:start
TO LANDING

00:12:55.164 --> 00:12:56.165 position:24% line:89% align:start
Come in. Welcome.

00:13:03.572 --> 00:13:05.574 position:13% line:83% align:start
Gimme a Maou Gaisen on the
rocks.

00:13:07.743 --> 00:13:09.077 position:27% line:89% align:start
Certainly, sir.

00:13:10.478 --> 00:13:13.281 position:5% line:83% align:start
To think, I'd find you here, in
Japan.

00:13:15.750 --> 00:13:20.421 position:7% line:77% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>Despite everything</i>
 <i>that's  happened, we're</i>
 <i>returning to Mars.</i>

00:13:22.589 --> 00:13:24.091 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>You look surprised.</i>

00:13:26.593 --> 00:13:29.797 position:5% line:89% align:start
(KOU) <i>I beg your pardon, sir...?</i>

00:13:32.699 --> 00:13:34.868 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're talking to the current
Deputy Commander...

00:13:35.601 --> 00:13:38.371 position:7% line:83% align:start
...of the Annex 1 project at
U-NASA.

00:13:38.905 --> 00:13:41.874 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm a major with the Japanese
Air Self Defense Force.

00:13:42.809 --> 00:13:44.777 position:10% line:89% align:start
The name's Shichsei Hiruma.

00:13:47.612 --> 00:13:49.181 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>And you're Professor Honda...</i>

00:13:50.282 --> 00:13:51.116 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Correct?</i>

00:13:56.455 --> 00:13:59.624 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Twenty years ago, on the Bugs 2</i>
 <i>mission</i>

00:14:00.826 --> 00:14:02.761 position:5% line:89% align:start
...you were a project engineer.

00:14:03.394 --> 00:14:09.467 position:5% line:77% align:start
You tried to outsmart the other
nations, as well as Komachi.
But you failed.

00:14:10.835 --> 00:14:14.237 position:10% line:83% align:start
You also used...my brother,
Ichiro Hiruma.

00:14:16.639 --> 00:14:19.342 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm surprised you're still
alive, Professor Honda.

00:14:22.645 --> 00:14:25.482 position:10% line:89% align:start
But...I'm glad that you are.

00:14:27.650 --> 00:14:31.620 position:13% line:77% align:start
I didn't come here as an
official representative of
U-NASA.

00:14:32.554 --> 00:14:37.559 position:5% line:77% align:start
As I mentioned, my true role is
to defend the country of
Japan.

00:14:38.660 --> 00:14:40.629 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>For that, I need your </i>
 <i>cooperation.</i>

00:14:40.863 --> 00:14:42.831 position:5% line:89% align:start
And I also need your knowledge.

00:14:43.764 --> 00:14:45.933 position:7% line:83% align:start
But, as they say, first things
first...

00:14:47.802 --> 00:14:52.372 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>You need to understand the </i>
 <i>difference...between the Bugs</i>
 <i>Project and the Annex Project.</i>

00:14:59.813 --> 00:15:00.647 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sheila!

00:15:01.882 --> 00:15:03.182 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:15:03.416 --> 00:15:05.919 position:21% line:89% align:start
Here goes nothing!

00:15:05.952 --> 00:15:08.855 position:5% line:83% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Attention, everyone.</i>
 <i>This is  your captain speaking.</i>

00:15:10.356 --> 00:15:13.692 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>We've now been traveling for a </i>
 <i>total of thirty-nine days.</i>

00:15:14.994 --> 00:15:19.698 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>The mission's progressing </i>
 <i>smoothly, and we'll be entering</i>
 <i>Mars's atmosphere shortly.</i>

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:24.202 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Everyone assemble in Area A in </i>
 <i>two hours.</i>

00:15:25.537 --> 00:15:27.705 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Following the equipment</i>
 <i>inspection...</i>

00:15:28.373 --> 00:15:31.543 position:5% line:83% align:start
...we will begin Plan Alpha to
land on Mars.

00:15:36.848 --> 00:15:40.851 position:19% line:77% align:start
Are you sure, Sheila?
You even learned Japanese from
Akari.

00:15:42.653 --> 00:15:43.587 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah

00:15:47.891 --> 00:15:51.394 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>I'm trying my best to put on a </i>
 <i>sympathetic face</i>

00:15:52.562 --> 00:15:54.730 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>...but I'm really just hiding my</i>
 <i>fear.</i>

00:15:56.399 --> 00:15:58.568 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>I can't be the only one...</i>

00:16:00.402 --> 00:16:03.238 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>Once all of us get to Mars...</i>

00:16:06.575 --> 00:16:08.910 position:24% line:89% align:start
 Are you frightened, Eva?

00:16:09.744 --> 00:16:11.713 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing]

00:16:13.048 --> 00:16:17.751 position:16% line:77% align:start
No matter what happens,
you must understand that fear is
a gift.

00:16:18.053 --> 00:16:20.588 position:24% line:89% align:start
[exhaling slowly]

00:16:22.890 --> 00:16:30.463 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>If there's one natural defense </i>
 <i>we possess as humans, it's our </i>
 <i>ability to experience fear well</i>
 <i>before death's grasp.</i>

00:16:30.931 --> 00:16:35.268 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Allowing us to face our fears. </i>
 <i>So we can devise a plan.</i>

00:16:36.436 --> 00:16:40.272 position:5% line:83% align:start
We officers are aware of how to
defeat these things.

00:16:42.441 --> 00:16:44.443 position:24% line:89% align:start
Rest assured, Eva.

00:16:46.745 --> 00:16:55.419 position:7% line:71% align:start
You may have ninety-nine peers.
But, you have one hundred
people to help you face and
fight against your fears...

00:16:57.622 --> 00:16:59.957 position:24% line:89% align:start
Even then...No...!

00:17:01.792 --> 00:17:04.462 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>I hope we never land on Mars!</i>

00:17:06.631 --> 00:17:08.465 position:13% line:83% align:start
(SHOLICHI) <i>Michelle! Got a</i>
 <i>moment?</i>

00:17:09.100 --> 00:17:09.800 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:17:11.668 --> 00:17:15.305 position:19% line:77% align:start
 <i>Several security camera in</i>
 <i>Areas D and S are down. </i>
 <i>Can you go check it out?</i>

00:17:17.841 --> 00:17:18.074 position:35% line:89% align:start
[spitting]

00:17:18.908 --> 00:17:19.509 position:35% line:89% align:start
So, uh...

00:17:20.610 --> 00:17:22.378 position:5% line:83% align:start
...who do you think's still in
there taking a shower?

00:17:22.711 --> 00:17:24.981 position:10% line:83% align:start
I saw that Chinese girl go in
earlier.

00:17:25.481 --> 00:17:26.982 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Whoever it is, it's been a </i>
 <i>while.</i>

00:17:27.650 --> 00:17:31.319 position:10% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Huh, you smell that?</i>
 <i>There's a scent...</i>

00:17:31.987 --> 00:17:35.824 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's not quite like shampoo, but</i>
 <i>it's feminine.</i>

00:17:37.126 --> 00:17:37.993 position:50% line:89% align:start
(MARCOS) <i>Yeah...</i>

00:17:40.294 --> 00:17:44.499 position:13% line:71% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Well,...it's only</i>
 <i>natural, right? To want to check</i>
 <i>things out and make sure</i>
 <i>everything's okay?</i>

00:17:45.066 --> 00:17:47.001 position:19% line:89% align:start
(MARCOS) <i>Oh, yeah, totally!</i>

00:17:51.605 --> 00:17:52.506 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chortle]

00:17:54.041 --> 00:17:59.513 position:5% line:77% align:start
Oh! I was just, uh, worried that
 you might've passed out or
something, so...

00:18:00.013 --> 00:18:01.347 position:30% line:89% align:start
M-my mistake!

00:18:03.516 --> 00:18:04.183 position:27% line:89% align:start
[thud and groan]

00:18:04.216 --> 00:18:04.684 position:38% line:89% align:start
[outcry]

00:18:05.518 --> 00:18:06.352 position:21% line:89% align:start
[insect-like chirp]

00:18:12.858 --> 00:18:17.462 position:5% line:83% align:start
Those things find their way into
 practically everything...

00:18:21.499 --> 00:18:21.833 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:18:26.004 --> 00:18:27.806 position:30% line:89% align:start
Wha-?! What?!

00:18:27.839 --> 00:18:30.574 position:7% line:83% align:start
But this isn't Mars! How did
they-?!

00:18:31.042 --> 00:18:32.643 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crash]

00:18:34.179 --> 00:18:35.546 position:30% line:5% align:start
 <i>It's a miracle</i>

00:18:37.047 --> 00:18:38.716 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>How did I dodge that?!</i>

00:18:39.717 --> 00:18:43.053 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>Like a cockroach scurrying out</i>
 <i>from underneath a swift blow</i>

00:18:44.554 --> 00:18:46.389 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>The cards are stacked against us</i>

00:18:47.724 --> 00:18:48.558 position:38% line:89% align:start
Marcos!

00:18:49.559 --> 00:18:50.960 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'll keep this thing busy.

00:18:51.594 --> 00:18:53.062 position:13% line:89% align:start
You get to the cargo hold!

00:18:53.563 --> 00:18:54.797 position:10% line:83% align:start
But what are... what are you
gonna-?!

00:18:56.032 --> 00:18:58.567 position:5% line:83% align:start
If we try to make a run for it,
it'll kill us both! Now go!

00:18:59.768 --> 00:19:00.669 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:02.070 --> 00:19:03.972 position:16% line:89% align:start
Come on, you! Bring it!

00:19:09.510 --> 00:19:09.745 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:19:12.646 --> 00:19:13.948 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insect squeaking]

00:19:13.981 --> 00:19:15.583 position:35% line:89% align:start
Michelle!

00:19:15.616 --> 00:19:16.751 position:27% line:89% align:start
Go after Marcos.

00:19:18.486 --> 00:19:21.922 position:5% line:77% align:start
No way! I'm not letting you do
this alone! The others are
helpless without the serum.

00:19:21.956 --> 00:19:24.524 position:5% line:83% align:start
Their new abilities are useless
to them!

00:19:24.557 --> 00:19:25.658 position:19% line:89% align:start
They've got nothing!

00:19:27.228 --> 00:19:30.430 position:19% line:77% align:start
It's just you and me,
we're the only ones born with
superhuman abilities!

00:19:31.664 --> 00:19:32.665 position:27% line:89% align:start
You have to go.

00:19:32.866 --> 00:19:33.600 position:38% line:89% align:start
What...?

00:19:35.001 --> 00:19:37.736 position:10% line:77% align:start
If there's more than one of
these Terraformars, Marcos is
a goner.

00:19:38.104 --> 00:19:39.605 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>You must protect him.</i>

00:19:39.838 --> 00:19:41.774 position:13% line:89% align:start
Can there...really be...?!

00:19:42.141 --> 00:19:43.275 position:16% line:89% align:start
[gushing and crunching]

00:19:43.308 --> 00:19:48.013 position:7% line:89% align:start
[choking, gasping for breath]

00:19:48.046 --> 00:19:53.684 position:27% line:89% align:start
[thud, choking]

00:19:53.718 --> 00:19:54.119 position:38% line:89% align:start
[splat]

00:19:55.154 --> 00:19:57.622 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:19:57.655 --> 00:20:00.925 position:7% line:83% align:start
We've gotta find some place to
take cover!

00:20:00.958 --> 00:20:06.530 position:27% line:89% align:start
[muffled cries]

00:20:06.563 --> 00:20:09.633 position:16% line:89% align:start
[insect-like chittering]

00:20:10.600 --> 00:20:11.034 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:20:11.568 --> 00:20:15.638 position:35% line:89% align:start
[wailing]

00:20:15.672 --> 00:20:16.072 position:44% line:89% align:start
Where's the serum!

00:20:16.672 --> 00:20:17.673 position:5% line:89% align:start
In the cargo hold!

00:20:17.974 --> 00:20:19.775 position:35% line:89% align:start
Get back!

00:20:19.809 --> 00:20:21.178 position:35% line:89% align:start
But that's just a...!

00:20:21.610 --> 00:20:23.813 position:5% line:83% align:start
just a riot gun. Yeah, I'm aware
of that!

00:20:24.280 --> 00:20:26.048 position:13% line:89% align:start
This thing's gotta die...

00:20:26.081 --> 00:20:27.249 position:7% line:89% align:start
...and this is all I've got!

00:20:31.220 --> 00:20:33.655 position:5% line:83% align:start
Somebody! Get to the cargo hold
fast!

00:20:37.293 --> 00:20:38.493 position:35% line:5% align:start
 <i>The serum</i>

00:20:39.994 --> 00:20:43.832 position:5% line:83% align:start
For close-quarters combat with
a Terraformar, use the serum.

00:20:45.332 --> 00:20:48.136 position:5% line:83% align:start
Now, your body will struggle to
adapt to it at first...

00:20:48.735 --> 00:20:51.839 position:7% line:83% align:start
...but the serum will awaken
your new abilities.

00:20:53.841 --> 00:20:56.576 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>If only I had that damn serum</i>

00:20:57.945 --> 00:21:07.954 position:16% line:89% align:start
[bellowing and shooting]

00:21:07.987 --> 00:21:16.761 position:16% line:89% align:start
[bellowing and shooting]

00:21:16.962 --> 00:21:17.929 position:27% line:89% align:start
[inhales deeply]

00:21:17.963 --> 00:21:21.166 position:13% line:89% align:start
[boom, cracking, groaning]

00:21:23.168 --> 00:21:23.734 position:41% line:89% align:start
[bang]

00:21:24.870 --> 00:21:25.971 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh,...God!

00:21:30.908 --> 00:21:31.675 position:21% line:89% align:start
[juicy smack, whack]

00:21:31.709 --> 00:21:31.876 position:41% line:89% align:start
God-!

00:21:32.309 --> 00:21:33.344 position:27% line:89% align:start
[squelsh, thud]

00:21:33.376 --> 00:21:36.881 position:24% line:89% align:start
[plop, whimpering]

00:21:40.217 --> 00:21:41.285 position:30% line:89% align:start
Let's open it.

00:21:41.718 --> 00:21:42.152 position:24% line:89% align:start
[shaky breathing]

00:21:42.685 --> 00:21:43.853 position:21% line:89% align:start
[hydraulic hissing]

00:21:43.887 --> 00:21:45.655 position:27% line:89% align:start
[deep inhaling]

00:21:45.688 --> 00:21:56.565 position:19% line:89% align:start
[clattering, smashing]

00:21:58.800 --> 00:22:02.371 position:7% line:89% align:start
[insect chattering, breaking]

00:22:02.403 --> 00:22:04.239 position:7% line:83% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Washington, this is</i>
 <i>Annex 1.</i>

00:22:04.940 --> 00:22:09.110 position:21% line:89% align:start
The Annex Project...

00:22:09.143 --> 00:22:10.312 position:30% line:89% align:start
...has failed.

